      Part4: 3030757262
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: "...You do seem reliable. \nPlease, forgive my manners, but a man
      can't lower his guard at times like this, what with those... yankees hiding
      everywhere... "
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828017927
    - rid: 5324356914828017928
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 1033, y: 92}
    guid:
      Part1: 2581309536
      Part2: 1215088153
      Part3: 3417071789
      Part4: 2136760882
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: 'Which is why you can''t go places unless you''re properly equipped.

      I''ve
      recently purchased a new weapon and I''ve been waiting for a chance to use
      it on some of those pigs.

      If you happen to know anything about that...
      Whistle and I''ll do what a good comrade must.'
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828017930
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2363, y: 173}
    guid:
      Part1: 3427183337
      Part2: 1112303659
      Part3: 3191303844
      Part4: 499014773
    tag: 
  - dialogueText: '...Not what a real comrade would say.

      I think you have
      yet to experience what this world has to offer, and I envy you for that.

      Then
      again, I don''t think we have much in common if that''s the case.'
    doesItProveAnything: 0
    responses:
    - rid: 5324356914828017932
    isRootNode: 0
    editorPosition: {x: 2363, y: -25.999987}
    guid:
      Part1: 3584792841
      Part2: 1107239334
      Part3: 3147153559
      Part4: 527083217
    tag: 
